OL,3,CConservative candidate withdraws over
OL,4,C'wholly inappropriate' online posts
OL,6,FMr Trask withdrew as a candidate after
OL,7,FThe Mirror reported on posts he
OL,8,Fallegedly made on a fitness forum in
OL,9,F2013, making sexually explicit
OL,10,Fcomments about women.
OL,12,FIn a statement, Sam Trask said: "These
OL,13,Fcomments were made a number of years
OL,14,Fago, and I recognise they are wholly
OL,15,Finappropriate. For that I apologise
OL,16,Fand have decided to withdraw as a
OL,17,Fcandidate."
